CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Jones Lang LaSalle provides a wide range of real estate-related services to owners, occupiers, and investors worldwide, including leasing, property and project management, and capital markets advisory. JLL's investment management arm, LaSalle Investment Management, manages over $70 billion for clients across diverse public and private real estate strategies.
